 ### Vaultwarden

Purpose: Centralized password management

Technology: Vaultwarden (Bitwarden-compatible server)

Hosted On: apps.lab.local

Access: https://vault.lab.local

SSL: Encrypted via apps.lab.local certificate

Authentication: Master password (stored offline)

Description: Self-hosted password manager providing encrypted storage for all infrastructure credentials, service passwords, and personal accounts. Integrates with Ansible Vault for infrastructure automation secrets.

Key Features: - End-to-end encryption - Password generator - Folder organization - Secure notes - Browser extension support - Mobile app support

